<h1>Milestone Application Post Installation Instructions</h1>
<h1>To configure the Email To Task Service:</h1>
1. Go to Setup -> Develop -> Email Services
2. Click "New Email Service".
3. Give a Email Service Name "Email To Milestone Task".
4. Select the Apex Class "Milestone1_Email_Handler".
5. Set "Accept Attachments" to "All".
6. Set "Accept Email From" to "All Email Addresses".
7. Check "Active"
8. Set All Failure Response options to 'Bounce Message'.
9. Click "Save and New Email Address".
10. Setup A New Email Address.
